## Description
Adds will-change CSS hints for better animation performance on mobile.

## Problem
- Animations can cause jank on mobile devices
- Browser doesn't optimize transform/opacity changes
- GPU acceleration not triggered
- Poor scrolling/animation FPS

## Solution
- Add will-change: transform class
- Add will-change: opacity class
- Enable for animated elements only
- Browser can optimize rendering pipeline

## Impact
- Smoother animations on mobile
- Better scrolling performance
- GPU acceleration for transforms
- Reduced animation jank

## Usage
Add `will-change-transform` or `will-change-opacity` classes to animated elements, or use `data-animated="true"`.

